    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies the steps a host takes in deciding how to autoconfigure its interfaces in IP version 6.  The autoconfiguration process includes generating a link-local address, generating global addresses via stateless address autoconfiguration, and the Duplicate Address Detection procedure to verify the uniqueness of the addresses on a link. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
